1. Pineal gland (Melatonin)
2. Pituitary gland (Tropic hormones, Oxitocin, Vasopressin, ...)
3. Thyroid gland (Triiodothyroine, Thyroxine)
4. Thymus (Thymosin, T-cells)
5. Adrenal gland ((Nor)adrenalin, Corticosteroids, Androgens,...)
6. Pancreas (Insulin, Glucagon)
7. Ovary (Estrogen, Progesterone)
8. Testis (Testosterone)
